snippet.title: Kill ‘em All Release Trailer 2018
snippet.description:
Available now on: 

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/816870/Kill_Em_All/

Kill 'Em All is an fun aggressive first-person zombie survival shooter. It's a humble tribute to those evergreen FPS classics we all know & love. It features a Campaign with 10 mind-numbing levels with a neat range of weapons and an Arcade mode with endless waves of Zombies coming at you.

Developed by AppRoarr Studios

Facebook- https://www.facebook.com/approarr/
Twitter- https://twitter.com/AppRoarr
Website- www.approarr.com
